comment: I’m Korean, and my biggest dream was to see YE perform live, but I never thought it would actually happen. When I found out he was coming to Korea, I bought a ticket right away. I was so hyped I couldn’t even sleep, and after going to the listening party in Goyang, it honestly felt like I’d been to heaven. I was beyond happy, and I’m so thankful to YE and Ty$. YE, you’re my hero. Your music has gotten me through so much and has given me so much confidence. I wouldn’t be where I am today without it. I love you, and I hope you stay healthy for a long time. I’ll never forget the show in Korea. I even got YouTube Premium just so I could watch this video whenever I'm going through tough times. Thank you for everything!❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️🐐🐐🐐🐐🐐🤍🤍🤍
